description:
In this makeup tutorial for asian eyes, Pamela Hackeman, Instructor at Make-Up Designory's Los Angeles Campus, uses her favorite versatile travel palette to take a natural daytime beauty look and bump it up to a sexy evening fashion look with a smoky eye for Asian skin.

For more information about the products and techniques in this video, visit our blog: http://www.mudblog.net/blog/make-up_o...
